    <h3>More Parameters (1)</h3>

    <p>To pass more parameters in a context, use square brackets and commas, and single quotes for literals.</p>

    <p>For example <code>t:context="['view',personId]"</code>
    would render a URL like this: <code>http://thehost/jumpstart/examples/navigation/MoreParameters2/view/1</code>.</p>

    <div class="eg">
        <t:pagelink page="navigation/MoreParameters2" context="[anInt,aLong,aString,aDouble,aBigDecimal,aBoolean,aMode,'create']">
            Pass many parameters
        </t:pagelink><br/>
    </div>

